snippet.title: SELF - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
SELF is a Kafkaesque suspense text-based adventure game with simulation and puzzle mechanics.
Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1074170/SELF/
Itch.io: https://indienova.itch.io/self
Please consider adding it to your wishlists if you'd like to get a reminder when it's released.

It will be available on Nintendo Switch, Steam and Itch.io this year.
